<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>323</hymn_number>
<title>TLING TEIN KA ZUMH CH323</title>
<key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ka hngalh khawh lomi thil vialte, Jesuh sinah ka ratpi A bia-kamnak ka
 zumh caah, Lungtuai in ka um lai lo.

[C1]
   A bia kha a zummi ka si, Tling le fek tein ka zumh, A bia kha a
   zummi ka si, Tling le fek tein ka zumh.

[V2]
 Ka sualnak Jesuh cung ka chuan, Amah thi in a ka tawl, Keimah kha a ka
 thianter ko, Vancung a ka kalpi lai.

[C2]
   A bia kha a zummi ka si, Tling le fek tein ka zumh, A bia kha a
   zummi ka si, Tling le fek tein ka zumh.

[V3]
 Ka ralchiatnak Jesuh ka pek, amah kha ka hngatchan ko, Khuamui lam ah
 ka um nain, A ceunak cu a maw lo.

[C3]
   A bia kha a zummi ka si, Tling le fek tein ka zumh, A bia kha a
   zummi ka si, Tling le fek tein ka zumh.

[V4]
 Ka tha-nuamnak Jesuh ka pek, Kaa lawmhnak Bawipa a si; Vawlei vialte
 Bawipa a si, Ka tummi kha a ngeih dih;

[C4]
   A bia kha a zummi ka si, Tling le fek tein ka zumh, A bia kha a
   zummi ka si, Tling le fek tein ka zumh.

[V5]
 Ka zeizong te Jesuh ka pek, Ka pum le ka thlarau zong, Ka ngeihmi le
 ka hmuh laimi, Jesuh kha ka chanh dih lai.

[C5]
   A bia kha a zummi ka si, Tling le fek tein ka zumh, A bia kha a
   zummi ka si, Tling le fek tein ka zumh.</lyrics>
</song>